Callback method to be invoked when an item in this widget has been clicked and held.

Parameters:
pParentThe AbsListWidget where the click happened
pWidgetThe widget within the AbsListWidget that was clicked
positionThe position of the widget in the list
idThe row id of the item that was clicked
